  "details": "The optional Paragraphs Library module allows the reuse of paragraphs in multiple places.  \nThe module doesn't sufficiently restrict access to unpublished library items in lists.  \nThis vulnerability is mitigated by the fact the paragraphs\\_library module must be in use, and that an attacker must have access to a list of library items, such as a field with autocomplete suggestions or a view.",
